text: Châtonnaye (Dictionnaire-Dikchenéro: Français-Patois/Patê-Franché. Société cantonale des patoisans fribourgeois. Fribourg: 2013. p. 103) is a municipality in the district of Glâne in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Municipalities in Glâne
